ğŸ“ HOW STACK WORKS (REAL FLOW)

        void a() {
            b();
        }

        void b() {
            c();
        }

        void c() {
        }

        Execution order:
            a() â†’ b() â†’ c()

        Stack growth:
            Frame for c()
            Frame for b()
